column5: Is there any store in VBay or Dryden to buy Dry Ice?
If your are on the 105, Red Lake road, Dutchies has dry ice.
Smitties and 4 Seasons in Ear Falls has Dry Ice. Don't choke... but it's around $4-5 per pound.
Last year Bobbie's was not selling dry ice. There is a place between V. Bay and Dryden that does - on the south side of the highway. I'm sure VBay Gord can help us with the name of the place.-
Eagle Junction Sore .. It is about 10 miles East of Vermilion Bay ..On the south side of Hwy #17
Thanks for all the answers!! Larry S
